kentik-device-onboarder (1.1.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Runtime: install ProxyHandler in the urllib opener so HTTPS_PROXY /
    HTTP_PROXY / NO_PROXY env vars in onboarder.env are honored for all
    Kentik API calls. Cloud metadata probes (169.254.x, 168.63.129.16)
    always bypass the proxy so DNS auto-detect keeps working.
  * Postinst: DNS preflight resolves the configured Kentik API host,
    healthcheck host, and (when set) HTTP proxy host immediately after
    writing onboarder.env, surfacing 'name or service not known' at
    install time. Non-fatal.
  * Bump installer User-Agent to kentik-device-onboarder-installer/1.1.4.

 -- Kentik Technologies, Inc. <support@kentik.com>  Thu, 14 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000

